 \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 5\right)\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 5\right)\]
 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(4 x + 5\right) \left(9 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(6 x + 6\right) \left(8 x + 7\right) - \left(7 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 2\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(2 x^{2} + x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 6 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[- \left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 4 x + 8\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[- \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 2 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x^{2} + 3 x + 4\right) - \left(8 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} \left(- x^{2} - 2 x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[- \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(10 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[4 x \left(7 x^{2} + 6 x + 2\right) + \left(7 x + 5\right) \left(8 x + 4\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- 3 x - 7\right) \left(2 x^{2} + 2 x + 9\right) + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 9 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 1\right) \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} - \left(7 x + 10\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 6 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 7 x - 5\right) \left(9 x + 3\right) + \left(6 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x + 8\right) - \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 9\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(8 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(- 6 x^{2} - x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(4 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 7\right) + \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 4 x^{2} - 2 x - 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 2 x + 3\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 5\right)\]
 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(4 x + 5\right) \left(9 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(6 x + 6\right) \left(8 x + 7\right) - \left(7 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 2\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(2 x^{2} + x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 6 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[- \left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 4 x + 8\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[- \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 2 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x^{2} + 3 x + 4\right) - \left(8 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} \left(- x^{2} - 2 x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[- \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(10 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[4 x \left(7 x^{2} + 6 x + 2\right) + \left(7 x + 5\right) \left(8 x + 4\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- 3 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(4 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 7\right) + \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 4 x^{2} - 2 x - 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x -  \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 5\right)\]
 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(4 x + 5\right) \left(9 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(6 x + 6\right) \left(8 x + 7\right) - \left(7 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 2\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(2 x^{2} + x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 6 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[- \left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 4 x + 8\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[- \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 2 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x^{2} + 3 x + 4\right) - \left(8 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} \left(- x^{2} - 2 x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[- \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(10 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[4 x \left(7 x^{2} + 6 x + 2\right) + \left(7 x + 5\right) \left(8 x + 4\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- 3 x - 7\right) \left(2 x^{2} + 2 x + 9\right) + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 9 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 1\right) \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} - \left(7 x + 10\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 6 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 7 x - 5\right) \left(9 x + 3\right) + \left(6 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x + 8\right) - \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 9\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(8 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(- 6 x^{2} - x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(4 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 7\right) + \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 4 x^{2} - 2 x - 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 2 x + 3\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]
 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Durs}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(- 24 x + \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(- 36 x + \left(- 26 x - 61\right) \left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} - 32\right) - 16\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(6 x + 5\right) \left(16 x + \left(9 x + 9\right) \left(- 48 x + \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 63 x + \left(9 x + 8\right)^{2} - 45\right) - 36\right) + 80\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 15 x + \left(4 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(42 x + \left(7 x^{2} + 9\right) \left(- 20 x + \left(5 x + 6\right)^{2} - 30\right) + 48\right) - 30\right) \left(x^{2} + 6 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(9 x + 10\right) \left(- 25 x + \left(- 54 x + \left(- 7 x - 40\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} - 36\right) \left(x^{2} + 5 x + 8\right) - 30\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \left(- 60 x + \left(4 x + 7\right) \left(- 63 x + \left(- 91 x - 36\right) \left(2 x + 2\right) - 49\right) - 20\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(4 x + 1\right)^{2} \left(- 27 x + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(- 70 x + \left(x + 9\right) \left(- 45 x + \left(5 x + 3\right)^{2} - 24\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 9 x + 3\right) - 40\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 5 x + 3\right) + 20\right) \left(9 x^{2} + x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(10 x + 5\right) \left(- 16 x + \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(- 12 x + \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(- 40 x + \left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} - 40\right) - 20\right) - 20\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \left(- 30 x + \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 50 x + \left(4 x^{2} - 23 x\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 7 x + 1\right) - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x -  \section{Exercices de In\'equation Durs}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[\frac{9 x^{2} + 30 x + 25}{7 x + 6} \leq \frac{9 x^{2} - 30 x + 25}{7 x + 6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\frac{4 x + 4}{3 x + 6} \leq \frac{2 x + 9}{9 x + 4}\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[\frac{9 x + 9}{9 x + 1} \geq \frac{7 x + 10}{6 x + 3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\frac{8 x + 1}{9 x + 8} \geq \frac{7 x + 4}{7 x + 2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\frac{16 x^{2} - 16 x + 4}{9 x + 5} \geq \frac{16 x^{2} - 32 x + 16}{9 x + 5}\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[\frac{4 x^{2} - 4 x + 1}{9 x + 6} \geq \frac{4 x^{2} - 8 x + 4}{9 x + 6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[\frac{3 x + 1}{5 x + 5} \leq \frac{7 x + 4}{4 x + 6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\frac{3 x + 3}{2 x + 1} \leq \frac{x + 5}{2 x + 5}\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\frac{25 x^{2} - 30 x + 9}{3 x + 2} \geq \frac{25 x^{2} + 10 x + 1}{3 x + 2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\frac{9 x + 7}{8 x + 2} \geq \frac{10 x + 7}{4 x + 10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\frac{9 x^{2} - 30 x + 25}{4 x + 5} \leq \frac{x^{2} - 4 x + 4}{4 x + 5}\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\frac{9 x^{2} - 30 x + 25}{5 x + 5} \leq \frac{4 x^{2} - 16 x + 16}{5 x + 5}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\frac{2 x + 8}{x + 5} \geq \frac{8 x + 1}{8 x + 10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[\frac{5 x + 2}{5 x + 5} \geq \frac{x + 9}{8 x + 10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\frac{3 x + 4}{8 x + 8} \geq \frac{6 x + 10}{6 x + 2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\frac{x^{2} - 6 x + 9}{7 x + 10} \leq \frac{16 x^{2} - 16 x + 4}{7 x + 10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[\frac{9 x + 3}{10 x + 9} \leq \frac{10 x + 4}{3 x + 9}\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[\frac{16 x^{2} - 8 x + 1}{9 x + 2} \geq \frac{x^{2} - 6 x + 9}{9 x + 2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[\frac{x^{2} - 8 x + 16}{5 x + 4} \leq \frac{9 x^{2} - 12 x + 4}{5 x + 4}\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[\frac{6 x + 6}{5 x + 10} \geq \frac{4 x + 3}{9 x + 2}\]

 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 63\right) - 70\right) - 36\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 48 x + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(- 16 x + \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(41 x + 35\right) - 64\right) - 32\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(6 x + \left(- 32 x + \left(- 42 x + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} - 90\right) + 63\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 48 x + \left(- 24 x + \left(- 80 x + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} - 60\right) \left(2 x^{2} + 6 x + 7\right) - 18\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 4 x + 1\right) -  \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} \left(- x^{2} - 2 x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[- \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(10 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[4 x \left(7 x^{2} + 6 x + 2\right) + \left(7 x + 5\right) \left(8 x + 4\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- 3 x - 7\right) \left(2 x^{2} + 2 x + 9\right) + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 9 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 1\right) \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} - \left(7 x + 10\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 6 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 7 x - x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(4 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 7\right) + \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 4 x^{2} - 2 x - 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 2 x + 3\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]

 \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]
 \section{Exercices de In\'equation Moyens}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[\frac{2 x + 9}{2 x + 6} \leq \frac{\sqrt{30} \pi}{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\frac{8 x + 10}{x + 7} \geq \frac{\sqrt{30}}{3 \pi}\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[\frac{6 x + 5}{9 x + 7} \leq 2 \sqrt{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\frac{6 x + 5}{8 x + 2} \leq \frac{\sqrt{30}}{6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\frac{4 x + 8}{9 x + 2} \geq \frac{2 \sqrt{3}}{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[\frac{7 x + 2}{9 x + 6} \geq \frac{\sqrt{114}}{6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[\frac{5 x + 2}{3 x + 4} \geq \frac{\sqrt{5}}{10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\frac{7 x + 4}{9 x + 1} \leq \frac{\pi}{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\frac{9 x + 5}{6 x + 7} \geq \frac{\sqrt{77}}{11}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\frac{4 x + 10}{7 x + 10} \geq 3 \sqrt{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\frac{2 x + 2}{4 x + 2} \geq \sqrt{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\frac{2 x + 7}{x + 5} \leq \frac{\sqrt{7}}{7}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\frac{2 x + 6}{3 x + 1}  \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 5\right)\]
 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(4 x + 5\right) \left(9 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(6 x + 6\right) \left(8 x + 7\right) - \left(7 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 2\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(2 x^{2} + x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 6 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[- \left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 4 x + 8\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[- \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 2 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x^{2} + 3 x + 4\right) - \left(8 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} \left(- x^{2} - 2 x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[- \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(10 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[4 x \left(7 x^{2} + 6 x + 2\right) + \left(7 x + 5\right) \left(8 x + 4\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- 3 x - 7\right) \left(2 x^{2} + 2 x + 9\right) + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 9 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 1\right) \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} - \left(7 x + 10\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 6 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 7 x - 5\right) \left(9 x + 3\right) + \left(6 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x + 8\right) - \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 9\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(8 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(- 6 x^{2} - x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(4 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 7\right) + \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 4 x^{2} - 2 x - 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 2 x + 3\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 5\right)\]
 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(4 x + 5\right) \left(9 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(6 x + 6\right) \left(8 x + 7\right) - \left(7 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 2\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(2 x^{2} + x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 6 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[- \left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 4 x + 8\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[- \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 2 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x^{2} + 3 x + 4\right) - \left(8 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} \left(- x^{2} - 2 x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[- \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(10 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[4 x \left(7 x^{2} + 6 x + 2\right) + \left(7 x + 5\right) \left(8 x + 4\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- 3 x - 7\right) \left(2 x^{2} + 2 x + 9\right) + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 9 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 1\right) \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} - \left(7 x + 10\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 6 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 7 x - 5\right) \left(9 x + 3\right) + \left(6 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x + 8\right) - \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 9\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(8 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(- 6 x^{2} - x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(4 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 7\right) + \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 4 x^{2} - 2 x - 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x -  \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]
 \section{Exercices de In\'equation Moyens}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[\frac{2 x + 9}{2 x + 6} \leq \frac{\sqrt{30} \pi}{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\frac{8 x + 10}{x + 7} \geq \frac{\sqrt{30}}{3 \pi}\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[\frac{6 x + 5}{9 x + 7} \leq 2 \sqrt{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\frac{6 x + 5}{8 x + 2} \leq \frac{\sqrt{30}}{6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\frac{4 x + 8}{9 x + 2} \geq \frac{2 \sqrt{3}}{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[\frac{7 x + 2}{9 x + 6} \geq \frac{\sqrt{114}}{6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[\frac{5 x + 2}{3 x + 4} \geq \frac{\sqrt{5}}{10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\frac{7 x + 4}{9 x + 1} \leq \frac{\pi}{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\frac{9 x + 5}{6 x + 7} \geq \frac{\sqrt{77}}{11}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\frac{4 x + 10}{7 x + 10} \geq 3 \sqrt{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\frac{2 x + 2}{4 x + 2} \geq \sqrt{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\frac{2 x + 7}{x + 5} \leq \frac{\sqrt{7}}{7}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\frac{2 x + 6}{3 x + 1} \leq 1.0\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[\frac{6 x + 3}{9 x + 9} \leq \frac{\sqrt{70}}{7}\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\frac{10 x + 10}{6 x + 9} \geq \frac{\sqrt{2}}{6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\frac{8 x + 7}{8 x + 2} \geq \frac{4 \sqrt{11}}{11 \pi}\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[\frac{x + 2}{2 x + 3} \geq \frac{\pi}{4}\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[\frac{6 x + 6}{10 x + 1} \leq \frac{\sqrt{6}}{6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[\frac{x + 6}{9 x + 3} \geq \frac{\sqrt{77} \pi}{11}\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[\frac{10 x + 8}{8 x + 2} \geq \frac{\sqrt{6}}{6 \pi}\]In\'equation num\'ero 20 \[\frac{2 x + 8}{x + 5} \geq \frac{\sqrt{3} \pi}{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 21 \[\frac{10 x + 6}{5 x + 3} \leq \frac{\sqrt{13}}{3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 22 \[\frac{8 x + 8}{7 x + 9} \leq \frac{\sqrt{255}}{15}\]In\'equation num\'ero 23 \[\frac{2 x + 2}{3 x + 8} \leq 2 \sqrt{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 24 \[\frac{x + 9}{10 x + 5} \geq \frac{\sqrt{11} \pi}{11}\]In\'equation num\'ero 25  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x -  \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x - 3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 5\right)\]
 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(4 x + 5\right) \left(9 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(6 x + 6\right) \left(8 x + 7\right) - \left(7 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 2\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(2 x^{2} + x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 6 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[- \left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 4 x + 8\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[- \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 2 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x^{2} + 3 x + 4\right) - \left(8 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} \left(- x^{2} - 2 x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[- \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(10 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[4 x \left(7 x^{2} + 6 x + 2\right) + \left(7 x + 5\right) \left(8 x + 4\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- 3 x - 7\right) \left(2 x^{2} + 2 x + 9\right) + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 9 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 1\right) \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} - \left(7 x + 10\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 6 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 7 x - 5\right) \left(9 x + 3\right) + \left(6 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x + 8\right) - \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 9\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(8 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(- 6 x^{2} - x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(4 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 7\right) + \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 4 x^{2} - 2 x - 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 2 x + 3\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]
 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Durs}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(- 24 x + \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(- 36 x + \left(- 26 x - 61\right) \left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} - 32\right) - 16\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(6 x + 5\right) \left(16 x + \left(9 x + 9\right) \left(- 48 x + \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 63 x + \left(9 x + 8\right)^{2} - 45\right) - 36\right) + 80\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 15 x + \left(4 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(42 x + \left(7 x^{2} + 9\right) \left(- 20 x + \left(5 x + 6\right)^{2} - 30\right) + 48\right) - 30\right) \left(x^{2} + 6 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(9 x + 10\right) \left(- 25 x + \left(- 54 x + \left(- 7 x - 40\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} - 36\right) \left(x^{2} + 5 x + 8\right) - 30\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \left(- 60 x + \left(4 x + 7\right) \left(- 63 x + \left(- 91 x - 36\right) \left(2 x + 2\right) - 49\right) - 20\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(4 x + 1\right)^{2} \left(- 27 x + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(- 70 x + \left(x + 9\right) \left(- 45 x + \left(5 x + 3\right)^{2} - 24\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 9 x + 3\right) - 40\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 5 x + 3\right) + 20\right) \left(9 x^{2} + x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(10 x + 5\right) \left(- 16 x + \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(- 12 x + \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(- 40 x + \left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} - 40\right) - 20\right) - 20\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \left(- 30 x + \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 50 x + \left(4 x^{2} - 23 x\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 7 x + 1\right) - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x -  \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]

 \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Faciles}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(- 10 x - 8\right) \left(4 x + 9\right) + \left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 5 x - 5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x -
