3\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right) + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(6 x + 8\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(- 3 x - 10\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right) + \left(6 x + 10\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[\left(- 7 x - 4\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(7 x + 3\right) + \left(3 x + 7\right) \left(4 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(- 8 x - 10\right) \left(5 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(- 8 x - 4\right) \left(3 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 5 x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[\left(- 4 x - 2\right) \left(9 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 1\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[\left(- 6 x - 7\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 10\right) \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- x - 10\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(10 x + 8\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 9\right) \left(10 x + 3\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(6 x^{2} + 4 x + 6\right) + \left(x + 2\right) \left(x + 7\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(- 6 x - 3\right) \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 6\right) \left(3 x^{2} + 8 x + 5\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(- 10 x - 2\right) \left(x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(- 4 x - 10\right) \left(9 x + 6\right) + \left(7 x + 1\right) \left(6 x^{2} + x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(6 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x + 5\right)\]
 \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(4 x + 5\right) \left(9 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(6 x + 6\right) \left(8 x + 7\right) - \left(7 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 2\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(2 x^{2} + x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 6 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[- \left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 4 x + 8\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[- \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 2 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x^{2} + 3 x + 4\right) - \left(8 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} \left(- x^{2} - 2 x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[- \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(10 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[4 x \left(7 x^{2} + 6 x + 2\right) + \left(7 x + 5\right) \left(8 x + 4\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- 3 x - 7\right) \left(2 x^{2} + 2 x + 9\right) + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 9 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 1\right) \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} - \left(7 x + 10\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 6 x + 4\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 15 \[\left(- 7 x - 5\right) \left(9 x + 3\right) + \left(6 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 16 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x + 8\right) - \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 9\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 17 \[\left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} + \left(8 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(- 6 x^{2} - x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(4 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 7\right) + \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 4 x^{2} - 2 x - 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x - 5\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 2 x + 3\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right) \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

5\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 6 x + 8\right) + \left(3 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 3\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[\left(- 2 x - 9\right) \left(3 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 3\right) \left(4 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(- 8 x - 3\right) \left(7 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(x + 6\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(- 8 x - 5\right) \left(7 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(x + 1\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(- 2 x -  \section{Exercices de D\'eveloppement Moyens}D\'eveloppement num\'ero 0 \[\left(2 x + 2\right) \left(3 x + 9\right)^{2} - \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2} \cdot \left(7 x^{2} + 8 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 1 \[\left(- 3 x - 3\right) \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(2 x + 7\right) \left(4 x^{2} + 2 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 2 \[- \left(3 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} + \left(4 x + 2\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x + 2\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 3 \[\left(3 x + 5\right) \left(10 x + 4\right)^{2} - \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 4 \[\left(4 x + 5\right) \left(9 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 5 \[\left(6 x + 6\right) \left(8 x + 7\right) - \left(7 x + 4\right)^{2} \left(8 x + 2\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 6 \[\left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \left(10 x + 6\right)^{2} + \left(2 x^{2} + x + 7\right) \left(8 x^{2} + 6 x + 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 7 \[- \left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(2 x^{2} + 4 x + 8\right) + \left(7 x + 7\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 7\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 8 \[- \left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2} + \left(7 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(6 x^{2} + 2 x + 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 9 \[\left(4 x + 9\right)^{2} \cdot \left(5 x^{2} + 3 x + 4\right) - \left(8 x + 8\right)^{2} \cdot \left(10 x + 9\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 10 \[\left(x + 2\right)^{2} \left(5 x + 2\right)^{2} + \left(5 x + 10\right)^{2} \left(- x^{2} - 2 x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 11 \[- \left(6 x + 5\right)^{2} \left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} + \left(10 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x^{2} + 3 x + 8\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 12 \[4 x \left(7 x^{2} + 6 x + 2\right) + \left(7 x + 5\right) \left(8 x + 4\right)^{2}\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 13 \[\left(- 3 x - x - 1\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 18 \[\left(4 x + 3\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 7\right) + \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2} \left(- 4 x^{2} - 2 x - 6\right)\]D\'eveloppement num\'ero 19 \[\left(- 6 x -  \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de In\'equation Faciles}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[8 x + 10 \leq \left(5 x + 4\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\left(9 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 4 x^{2} + 9 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[5 x + 9 \geq 3 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\left(10 x + 2\right)^{2} \geq 3 x + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\left(10 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 2 x^{2} + 3 x\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[7 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \leq 8 x^{2} + 7\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[9 x + 8 \geq 7 x^{2} + 8 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\left(2 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq 6 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\left(6 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(x + 7\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\left(9 x + 1\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 6\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\left(10 x + 1\right)^{2} \leq 7 x + 4\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\left(5 x + 7\right)^{2} \leq \left(6 x + 1\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\left(5 x + 9\right)^{2} \leq \left(2 x + 5\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[3 x^{2} + 2 \geq 2 x^{2} + 8 x + 3\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\left(7 x + 9\right)^{2} \geq \left(8 x + 10\right)^{2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\left(6 x + 6\right)^{2} \leq 3 x + 8\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[2 x^{2} + 1 \leq 6 x + 9\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[7 x^{2} + 3 x + 6 \leq 4 x + 6\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[9 x + 1 \geq 2 x^{2} + 3 x + 5\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[3 x^{2} + 4 x + 8 \geq 6 x^{2} + 5 x\]\documentclass[a4paper,oneside,11pt]{article}

 \section{Exercices de In\'equation Durs}In\'equation num\'ero 0 \[\frac{9 x^{2} + 30 x + 25}{7 x + 6} \leq \frac{9 x^{2} - 30 x + 25}{7 x + 6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 1 \[\frac{4 x + 4}{3 x + 6} \leq \frac{2 x + 9}{9 x + 4}\]In\'equation num\'ero 2 \[\frac{9 x + 9}{9 x + 1} \geq \frac{7 x + 10}{6 x + 3}\]In\'equation num\'ero 3 \[\frac{8 x + 1}{9 x + 8} \geq \frac{7 x + 4}{7 x + 2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 4 \[\frac{16 x^{2} - 16 x + 4}{9 x + 5} \geq \frac{16 x^{2} - 32 x + 16}{9 x + 5}\]In\'equation num\'ero 5 \[\frac{4 x^{2} - 4 x + 1}{9 x + 6} \geq \frac{4 x^{2} - 8 x + 4}{9 x + 6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 6 \[\frac{3 x + 1}{5 x + 5} \leq \frac{7 x + 4}{4 x + 6}\]In\'equation num\'ero 7 \[\frac{3 x + 3}{2 x + 1} \leq \frac{x + 5}{2 x + 5}\]In\'equation num\'ero 8 \[\frac{25 x^{2} - 30 x + 9}{3 x + 2} \geq \frac{25 x^{2} + 10 x + 1}{3 x + 2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 9 \[\frac{9 x + 7}{8 x + 2} \geq \frac{10 x + 7}{4 x + 10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 10 \[\frac{9 x^{2} - 30 x + 25}{4 x + 5} \leq \frac{x^{2} - 4 x + 4}{4 x + 5}\]In\'equation num\'ero 11 \[\frac{9 x^{2} - 30 x + 25}{5 x + 5} \leq \frac{4 x^{2} - 16 x + 16}{5 x + 5}\]In\'equation num\'ero 12 \[\frac{2 x + 8}{x + 5} \geq \frac{8 x + 1}{8 x + 10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 13 \[\frac{5 x + 2}{5 x + 5} \geq \frac{x + 9}{8 x + 10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 14 \[\frac{3 x + 4}{8 x + 8} \geq \frac{6 x + 10}{6 x + 2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 15 \[\frac{x^{2} - 6 x + 9}{7 x + 10} \leq \frac{16 x^{2} - 16 x + 4}{7 x + 10}\]In\'equation num\'ero 16 \[\frac{9 x + 3}{10 x + 9} \leq \frac{10 x + 4}{3 x + 9}\]In\'equation num\'ero 17 \[\frac{16 x^{2} - 8 x + 1}{9 x + 2} \geq \frac{x^{2} - 6 x + 9}{9 x + 2}\]In\'equation num\'ero 18 \[\frac{x^{2} - 8 x + 16}{5 x + 4} \leq \frac{9 x^{2} - 12 x + 4}{5 x + 4}\]In\'equation num\'ero 19 \[\frac{6 x + 6}{5 x + 10} \geq \frac{4 x + 3}{9 x + 2}\]
 \section{Exercices de Tableaux de Variation Faciles}Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 0 \[f(x) = \left(8 \sqrt{3} \pi x + 3 \sqrt{3}\right)^{3}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 1 \[f(x) = \left(16 x + 16 \pi\right)^{3}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 2 \[f(x) = \sqrt{15} \pi x^{2} + x + \sqrt{2} \pi x + 2 + 2 \sqrt{2}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 3 \[f(x) = 16 x^{3} + 6 \pi x^{2} + 2 \sqrt{10} x + 8 \sqrt{3}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 4 \[f(x) = \left(5 \sqrt{6} x + 1\right)^{3}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 5 \[f(x) = \sqrt{13} x^{2} + 7 x + 3 \sqrt{2} \pi x + \sqrt{19} \pi\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 6 \[f(x) = 4 \sqrt{6} \pi x^{3} + 12 \sqrt{2} \pi x^{2} + 8 \sqrt{5} x + 16 \sqrt{3}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 7 \[f(x) = \left(2 x + 10\right) \left(5 x^{2} + 8 x + 1\right)\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 8 \[f(x) = x^{2} + 11 x + 7\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 9 \[f(x) = 18 \sqrt{2} x^{3} + 2 x^{2} + 12 \sqrt{3} \pi x + 2 \pi\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 10 \[f(x) = \sqrt{6} \pi x^{2} + \pi x + 9 x + 2 \sqrt{2} + 3\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 11 \[f(x) = \left(4 x + 5\right)^{2} \cdot \left(9 x + 9\right)\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 12 \[f(x) = \sqrt{14} \pi x^{2} + 6 x + \sqrt{10} \pi x + 6 + 2 \sqrt{3} \pi\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 13 \[f(x) = 2 \sqrt{5} \pi x^{2} + 6 x + 2 + \sqrt{6}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 14 \[f(x) = \left(9 \sqrt{11} x + 6 \sqrt{3} \pi\right)^{3}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 15 \[f(x) = 9 \pi x^{3} + 2 \pi x^{2} + 7 \sqrt{7} \pi x + 8 \pi\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 16 \[f(x) = \left(2 x + 4\right) \left(2 x + 7\right)\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 17 \[f(x) = 3 \pi x^{3} + 10 \pi x^{2} + 16 \sqrt{3} x + 8 \pi\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 18 \[f(x) = \left(2 x + 4\right)^{2} \cdot \left(3 x + 1\right)\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 19 \[f(x) = 2 x^{3} + \sqrt{3} \pi x^{2} + 2 x + \pi\]
 \section{Exercices de Tableaux de Variation Moyens}Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 0 \[f(x) = \left(7 x + 7\right) \sqrt{10 x + 6}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 1 \[f(x) = \frac{x + \sqrt{5} \pi}{x + 2 \sqrt{3} \pi}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 2 \[f(x) = \frac{\pi x + \sqrt{7}}{\sqrt{2} \pi x + \sqrt{19}}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 3 \[f(x) = \frac{\sqrt{13} \pi x + \sqrt{2}}{\sqrt{6} x + \sqrt{15}}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 4 \[f(x) = \frac{\sqrt{15} \pi x + 2 \sqrt{3} \pi}{2 \sqrt{5} x + 2 \sqrt{2} \pi}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 5 \[f(x) = \frac{\sqrt{6} \pi x + \pi}{\sqrt{6} \pi x + 2 \sqrt{5}}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 6 \[f(x) = \left(3 x + 9\right) \sqrt{8 x + 3}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 7 \[f(x) = \frac{\sqrt{10} \pi x + 2 \sqrt{3} \pi}{\sqrt{14} \pi x + \sqrt{19}}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 8 \[f(x) = \frac{\sqrt{13} \pi x + \pi}{\sqrt{2} \pi x + \sqrt{5} \pi}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 9 \[f(x) = \left(4 x + 7\right) \sqrt{7 x + 1}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 10 \[f(x) = \frac{\pi x + \sqrt{6} \pi}{3 x + \sqrt{15} \pi}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 11 \[f(x) = \sqrt{4 x + 8} \cdot \left(7 x + 7\right)\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 12 \[f(x) = \frac{\sqrt{10} x + 2 \sqrt{5} \pi}{x + \sqrt{13}}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 13 \[f(x) = \left(9 x + 2\right) \sqrt{9 x + 6}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 14 \[f(x) = \sqrt{x + 8} \cdot \left(3 x + 6\right)\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 15 \[f(x) = \sqrt{2 x + 4} \cdot \left(4 x + 9\right)\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 16 \[f(x) = \frac{\sqrt{7} \pi x + 1}{\sqrt{13} x + \sqrt{13}}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 17 \[f(x) = \frac{\sqrt{13} x + \sqrt{3}}{3 x + \sqrt{11} \pi}\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 18 \[f(x) = \sqrt{x + 1} \left(x + 7\right)\]Tableaux de Variation num\'ero 19 \[f(x) = \frac{2 x + \sqrt{7} \pi}{\sqrt{19} x + 3 \pi}\]
